115 void Agent::AddNeighbour(Agent &neighbour, float distSq)
116 {
117  float sightSq = param.sightRadius * param.sightRadius;
118 
119  if(distSq >= sightSq)
120  {
121  return;
122  }
123  int i = 0;
124  auto tmpit = Neighbours.begin();
125  while(tmpit != Neighbours.end() && i < param.agentsMaxNum && Neighbours[i].first < distSq)
126  {
127  i++;
128  tmpit++;
129  }
130  if(i < param.agentsMaxNum)
131  {
132  Neighbours.insert(tmpit,std::pair<float, Agent *>(distSq, &neighbour));
133  }
134 
135 }

150 void Agent::UpdateNeighbourObst()
151 {
152  NeighboursObst.clear();
153  std::vector<std::vector<ObstacleSegment>> tmpObstacles = map->GetObstacles();
154  float distSq = 0;
155 
156  for(int i = 0; i < tmpObstacles.size(); i++)
157  {
158  for(int j = 0; j < tmpObstacles[i].size(); j++)
159  {
160 
161  distSq = Utils::SqPointSegDistance(tmpObstacles[i][j].left, tmpObstacles[i][j].right, position);
162  if(distSq < maxSqObstDist)
163  {
164  NeighboursObst.push_back({distSq, tmpObstacles[i][j]});
165  }
166  }
167  }
168 
169  std::sort(NeighboursObst.begin(), NeighboursObst.end(), Utils::Less<ObstacleSegment>);
170 }
